title: The Green Grocer
description: Sells organic and locally produced products in a boutique-like setting in the historic Bay Centre building in downtown. From fresh produce to packaged and bulk items such as legumes, pasta, coffee, tea, herbs and spices. Other items include organic baby food, body, skin, hair and home care products as well as gluten-free items. Wine and artisan beer with tastings on Saturday afternoons (call ahead).
